snippet.title: Ten Dates - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1946070/Ten_Dates/

Ten Dates is the sequel to the interactive rom-com, Five Dates.

Misha, a millennial from London in search of that elusive in-person connection, tricks her best friend Ryan into going to a speed dating event with her. Each with their own five potential matches, Misha and Ryan must pluck up the courage and turn on the charm to date wildly different personalities.

Coming to PC, PS5, PS4, Xbox Series X, Xbox One, Nintendo Switch, iOS and Android 14/02/23.

Developed by GoodGate Media and Wales Interactive.
Published by Wales Interactive.
